{
  "stem": "24409.10",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, I can do it better, and I was made First Assistant Chief Interrogator.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I became the interrogator for the-- Chief Interrogator for the Malmedy Massacre case, which was a very hard position.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we brought 72 Germans to trial.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all found guilty. 40-some, 40 of them to hang, the others, life sentences, and 10 [? upwards ?] to 10 years.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was afterward a big stink, because the senator from this country, a young senator with the name of McCarthy, had received from some of his German constituents information that these prisoners were, the confessions, they were all achieved by torture, and by, by beatings, and so on.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he demanded an investigation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a big investigation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And being a European Jew, I was very much the, the chief interrogator.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very much in the limelight of the whole situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I explained to them that the, the committee understood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, of course, I didn't approach them with beatings or-- I wanted-- I hated them, yes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I hated them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wish every one of them would be dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I knew that actually I have to follow the rules.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
